data.text:
Show your support and raise awareness for breast cancer with our pink ribbon multicolored house flag. This flag features a vibrant design with a pink ribbon, the universal symbol of breast cancer awareness. It serves as a powerful reminder of the importance of early detection, support, and hope. Made from high-quality materials, our flags are durable and weather-resistant, ensuring they can withstand the elements. Display the Pink Ribbon flag proudly and join the fight against breast cancer.

Product Features:

Blue and pink ribbon house flag

House flag is accented with a ribbon symbolizes breast cancer awareness

Flags made from the high quality materials

UV, fade, and mildew resistant

Flags hang beautifully from a sewn-in sleeve

Brings decorative statements for any backyard, porch or veranda

Printed in the USA

Care instruction: machine washable

Fits most garden flag stands (not included)

Recommended for outdoor use only

Design is on one side only

Dimensions: 40" high x 28" wide

Material(s): polyester
